NOVIZIO FINANCIAL CONTEXT
Revenue model: Fashion DTC (transactional — each sale must be re-acquired) Key revenue lever: AOV (Average Order Value) — price mix and upsell drive this Seasonality: December typically 2x baseline — do not model as trend signal Margin benchmark: Fashion e-commerce GM target 40–60% ROAS threshold: < 3x → pause paid campaigns, diagnose before scaling 
NOVIZIO-SPECIFIC ASSUMPTIONS TO CHALLENGE
Product launch spikes are not trend signals — always separate launch revenue from baseline Repeat purchase rate is a leading indicator of brand health, not just a retention metric Inventory costs are often underestimated — include warehousing + returns in COGS model Influencer partnership ROI lags 4–6 weeks — do not attribute revenue to campaign week 
NEVER AGAIN — NOVIZIO
